### Anything else?

I feel like this could possibly be related to https://github.com/angular/angular/issues/54881.

The actual project I'm working on is where I'm emulating `NgComponentOutlet` by using `ViewContainerRef.createComponent` directly, and when I use `TemplateRef.createEmbeddedView` (instead of calling it on the view ref), and then attach it to the application ref, it seems to work.

This still seems like a bug to me though, or else I believe the documentation needs to be updated.

